  <section class="heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 align-middle">
          <div class="heading__subheadline">
            <h2>What is Pueblo Unido?</h2>
            <div class="horizontal-line">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="heading__text heading__text--medium-width">
            <p>Pueblo Unido is a non-profit organization that supports Portland metro community members in the fight against deportation. We connect clients to adequate legal representation and help gather evidence to strengthen cases against
              removal.
            </p>
            <a class="button" href="volunteer.html.en">Volunteer</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12 align-middle">
          <div class="video">
            <div class="video__media">
              <iframe title="About Pueblo Unido YouTube Video" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GJVg-gP4H2I" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-7 align-middle">
          <div class="heading__subheadline">
            <h2>Need Help?</h2>
            <div class="horizontal-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="heading__text">
            <p>Pueblo Unido provides legal service navigation and client advocate support for immigrants who are currently in removal proceedings. Those who are NOT currently in removal proceedings may contact Pueblo Unido for a list of nonprofit
            organizations
            in the Portland area who may be able to help.
            </p>
            <p>Don’t know whether you’re in removal proceedings or not? </p>
            <a class="button" href="get-help-detention.html.en">Facing Removal</a>
          </div>
          <div class="heading__text heading__text--small-disclaimer">
            <p>*Disclaimer*: Pueblo Unido PDX is not a law firm; we are not attorneys and we do not offer any legal advice. Instead, we help connect clients to experienced immigration attorneys and follow-up to ensure they receive the advice they
            are seeking.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 align-middle">
          <div class="heading__image">
            <img alt="Team Photo" src="./assets/images/pu-images/png/team--july.jpg" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-7 align-middle">
          <div class="heading__subheadline">
            <h2>Thank You - Second Annual Gala</h2>
            <div class="horizontal-line"></div>
          </div>
          <br />
          <p>To all of our generous donors as well as our wonderful volunteers, thank you for making our second annual
            gala a success. We reached our goal of $15,000 to continue to help community members out of detention
            and against deportation! We thrive because of the support we continue to gain from the 
            community and we can't wait to see you all next year!
          </p>
          <p>If you didn't get a chance to make it to the gala, we would like to encourage you to
            take this time to consider becoming a monthly donor to Pueblo Unido. A monthly donation helps 
            to consistently provide support to community members who are facing removal or currently in 
            detention.
          </p>
          <a class="button" target="blank" 
          href="https://secure.actblue.com/donate/pueblo-unido-pdx-1?refcode=website&recurring=1">Become a Monthly Donor</a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 align-middle">
          <div class="heading__image">
            <img src="./assets/images/pu-images/png/new/gala/guests-presentation--gala.jpg" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
